    <item>
      <title>委员会发现，盖茨在国会任职期间曾买通性服务并吸毒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/gaetz-paid-for-sex-used-drugs-while-in-congress-panel-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周一发布的两党委员会报告，众议院调查人员发现“大量证据”证明前众议员马特·盖茨在国会任职期间向多名女性（包括一名 17 岁女孩）支付性费用并购买和使用非法药物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/gaetz-paid-for-sex-used-drugs-while-in-congress-panel-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 17:07:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
